You said that you live on easy street, having money, car, delicious food, good clothes, good parents, cool friends, studying in a great school, and so on. Are you sure those are enough to make you have an adequate life? Or do you think that you're a good person just by paying lunch or just by buying clothes for your close friends? And you are happy if you are commended by others just because of those things?
I hope you can think twice for this.

Our life will be lovely if we can be useful for others. How much people out there that are starving, crying, shivering, and being lonely?
And if they need us?
Absolutely yes! Life will be very beautiful if we want to share with others, sharing happiness, knowledge, warmth, togetherness and many more. You can start with just a little thing, maybe by greeting them :)
Just try and you will get the joy!

Make them be happy, how nice and beautiful they are when they could laughing, being healthy, and being smart. I'm sure if we are not selfish and care with them, we could be together building a better life for all of us in this precious world from God!
